a:r.a:t: Timing in important with trademark applications. As soon as we have your instruction to proceed, we will prepare a trademark draft.
Active monitoring costs less than £30 a month and allows us to pick up any potential infringements whilst your trademark is in the appication stages
Representation gives you hours to use each month at heavily discounted rates for any trademark disputes, administration or enforcement.
Once you sign off the draft application, we will submit your fees and application to the trademark assessor for examination.
We can not claim any trademark rights until the application has been received and logged in the trademark journal (usually less than 21 days from application)
Once your application is in the journal you can put a TM logo next to your logo if you choose to, which means you have an application pending.
